    "Answer: [Yes] Justification: We state all assumptions and theoretical results in the main paper and provide their complete proofs in the appendix.",
    "Guidelines:• The answer NA means that the paper does not include theoretical results.• All the theorems, formulas, and proofs in the paper should be numbered and crossreferenced.",
